<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Project Handover & Documentation</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts for premium typography -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 20mm 20mm 20mm 20mm;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #334155;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        /* Header Layout */
        .doc-header {
            border-bottom: 3px solid #6366f1; /* Indigo theme for Handover */
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .doc-title-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 22pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .doc-subtitle {
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #6366f1;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
        }

        .doc-date {
            font-size: 9.5pt;
            color: #64748b;
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* Section Styling */
        h2 {
            font-size: 12pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            page-break-after: avoid;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 10.5pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6366f1;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            page-break-after: avoid;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        /* Highlight warning box */
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
            color: #991b1b;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }

        /* Standard Info Grid */
        .info-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
        }

        .info-col {
            width: 48%;
        }

        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 9.5pt;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
        }

        .info-value {
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        /* Code display styling */
        code, pre {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', Consolas, Monaco, monospace;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: #0f172a;
            font-size: 8.5pt;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        code {
            padding: 2px 5px;
        }

        pre {
            padding: 12px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            margin-top: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
        }

        /* Tables styling */
        .data-table {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }

        .data-table th {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: #475569;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 8px 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .data-table td {
            padding: 8px 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .data-table tr:nth-child(even) td {
            background-color: #fafbfc;
        }

        .security-action {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            color: #d97706;
            padding: 1px 4px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 7.5pt;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="doc-header">
        <div class="doc-title-container">
            <div>
                <h1 class="doc-title">Project Handover</h1>
                <div class="doc-subtitle">Credentials, Environments & Repository Handover</div>
            </div>
            <div class="doc-date">
                <strong>Handover Date:</strong> <%= date %><br>
                <strong>Project:</strong> <%= project.name %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-col">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">Developer:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= developer.name %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">Developer Contact:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= developer.email %></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-col">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">Client Name:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= client.name %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">Client Contact:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= client.email %></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="warning-box">
        <strong>SECURITY NOTICE:</strong> This document contains highly sensitive access credentials, API keys, and environment details. Upon receipt, the Client must change all default passwords, rotate API secrets immediately, and store this document in a secure credentials manager (e.g., 1Password, Bitwarden).
    </div>

    <p>This Handover Document signifies the official transfer of operational ownership of the <strong><%= project.name %></strong> application from the Developer to the Client. Below you will find technical resources, hosting access, environment variables, database details, and deployment guides required to maintain and run the software system.</p>

    <h2>1. Git Repository Access</h2>
    <p>The custom source code of the project has been pushed and is maintained in the following secure repository:</p>
    <table class="data-table">
        <tr>
            <td style="width: 25%; font-weight: 600;">Repository URL:</td>
            <td><code><%= git.url %></code></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="font-weight: 600;">Main/Production Branch:</td>
            <td><code><%= git.mainBranch || 'main' %></code></td>
        </tr>
        <% if (git.stagingBranch) { %>
            <tr>
                <td style="font-weight: 600;">Staging Branch:</td>
                <td><code><%= git.stagingBranch %></code></td>
            </tr>
        <% } %>
        <tr>
            <td style="font-weight: 600;">Transfer Status:</td>
            <td>Ownership transferred; Client developers invited as Administrators.</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>2. Deployment & Environments</h2>
    <p>The software is configured and deployed across the following hosting platforms:</p>
    <table class="data-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 20%;">Environment</th>
                <th style="width: 30%;">Hosting Provider</th>
                <th style="width: 50%;">Public URL / Access</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Production</strong></td>
                <td><%= deployment.productionHost || 'Not Specified' %></td>
                <td><a href="<%= deployment.productionUrl %>"><%= deployment.productionUrl %></a></td>
            </tr>
            <% if (deployment.stagingUrl) { %>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Staging / QA</strong></td>
                    <td><%= deployment.stagingHost || deployment.productionHost || 'Not Specified' %></td>
                    <td><a href="<%= deployment.stagingUrl %>"><%= deployment.stagingUrl %></a></td>
                </tr>
            <% } %>
            <% if (deployment.adminUrl) { %>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Admin Portal</strong></td>
                    <td><%= deployment.productionHost %></td>
                    <td><a href="<%= deployment.adminUrl %>"><%= deployment.adminUrl %></a></td>
                </tr>
            <% } %>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <h2>3. Application Credentials</h2>
    <p>Below is a summary of the accounts, hosting consoles, databases, and third-party dashboards created for this project:</p>
    
    <table class="data-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 25%;">Service Name</th>
                <th style="width: 30%;">Access URL / Console</th>
                <th style="width: 25%;">Admin User / Email</th>
                <th style="width: 20%;">Security Action Required</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <% credentials.forEach(function(cred) { %>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong><%= cred.service %></strong></td>
                    <td><code><%= cred.url %></code></td>
                    <td><%= cred.username %></td>
                    <td>
                        <% if (cred.actionRequired) { %>
                            <span class="security-action"><%= cred.actionRequired %></span>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <span class="security-action" style="background-color: #e2e8f0; color: #475569;">Review Account</span>
                        <% } %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            <% }); %>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>4. Environment Variables Configuration</h2>
    <p>The following variables must be configured in the production and staging environment settings (e.g. Vercel dashboard, AWS ECS, or `.env` configuration files) for the application to function correctly:</p>
    
    <table class="data-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 30%;">Variable Key</th>
                <th style="width: 45%;">Description / Purpose</th>
                <th style="width: 25%;">Default / Example Format</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <% environmentVariables.forEach(function(env) { %>
                <tr>
                    <td><code><%= env.key %></code></td>
                    <td><%= env.description %></td>
                    <td><code><%= env.exampleValue || '********' %></code></td>
                </tr>
            <% }); %>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>5. Local Developer Setup Guide</h2>
    <p>To run the application locally on a new workstation, follow these standard development configurations:</p>
    
    <h3>Prerequisites:</h3>
    <p>Ensure your machine has the following tools installed: Node.js (v<%= localSetup.nodeVersion || '18+' %>), npm / yarn, and git.</p>

    <h3>Setup Steps:</h3>
    <pre>
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone <%= git.url %>
cd <%= project.name.toLowerCase().replace(/\s+/g, '-') %>

# 2. Configure environment keys
cp .env.example .env
# (Open the .env file and fill in values from Section 4)

# 3. Install core dependencies
<%= localSetup.installCommand || 'npm install' %>

# 4. Start local database / migrations (if applicable)
<%= localSetup.dbCommand || 'npx prisma db push' %>

# 5. Run the local dev server
<%= localSetup.runCommand || 'npm run dev' %>
    </pre>

    <p style="font-size: 9.5pt; color: #475569; margin-top: 20px;">By executing the above steps, the local server will spin up on <code>http://localhost:3000</code>. For detailed API endpoints and controller models, refer to the inline comments in the repository code.</p>

</body>

</html>
